&lt;h2 id="solution">Solution &lt;a href="#solution" class="anchor" aria-hidden="true">&lt;i class="material-icons align-middle">link&lt;/i>&lt;/a>&lt;/h2>&lt;p>It&amp;rsquo;s a keyboard shortcut:&lt;/p>



 
 
 

 
 
 
 

 

 &lt;div class="prism-codeblock ">
 &lt;pre id="fda81d2" class="language- ">
 &lt;code>Ctrl &amp;#43; Alt &amp;#43; Backspace&lt;/code>
 &lt;/pre>
 &lt;/div>
&lt;p>This avoids having to type, for example:&lt;/p>



 
 
 

 
 
 
 

 

 &lt;div class="prism-codeblock ">
 &lt;pre id="c478ebf" class="language-bash ">
 &lt;code>/etc/init.d/gdm restart&lt;/code>
 &lt;/pre>
 &lt;/div>
&lt;p>That&amp;rsquo;s it, X restarts :-). &lt;strong>Warning, this should only be done while in X, otherwise the PC will reboot :-(&lt;/strong>.&lt;/p>
